metadata.name: improved financial fortune.
metadata.description:
Paintings of gods of good fortune are part of traditional culture around the world and are believed by many people.  This deity is said to bring good luck with money, and is especially worshiped by those who wish for prosperous business and improved financial fortune.

 Paintings of gods are often decorated with gold to symbolize abundance and prosperity, and can be seen in amulets and shrines.  It is believed that looking at this painting will bring good fortune, and many people use it in their daily lives.

 The picture of the god of improving financial luck focuses on obtaining material wealth, but behind it is also meant to encourage self-development and spiritual growth.  A picture of God like this is a wonderful existence that can give people hope and cultivate positive feelings.
